               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18371023-name-1177" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1177" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1177" type="surname" value="SCRIVENER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1177" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD SCRIVENER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am porter at Reeds and Co., of Aldennanbury. On the night of the 22nd of October I was near the Exchange, and felt my pocket picked—I turned round and looked, and the prisoner was running away—I called, "Stop thief," and pursued him—he was stopped, and the watchman produced my handkerchief—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18371023-name-1178" type="witnessName">
