                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1178" type="given" value="THOMAS BENJAMIN"></interp>THOMAS BENJAMIN MACKEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I was passing near the Exchange, and immediately followed the prisoner—I saw him throw the handkerchief</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183710230162"></xptr>
               <p>away when I was within a yard and a half of him—I did not lose sight of him at all—the officer took him.</p>
               <p>
