                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1179" type="given" value="PHILLIP"></interp>PHILLIP TURNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was on duty and heard the alarm, and saw the prisoner running—I stopped him, and took him to the station-house—I found the handkerchief by the Insurance office, when he had run, and where the witness pointed out.</p>
